{"tid":1694639,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賓特拿：我曾在訓練時叫亨利收嗲","createTime":"2019-11-05T08:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T16:23:57.000Z","uid":165817,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"58d7bd7f1ea1aa5c9832c33c91673fbfc1595d58","tid":1694639,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:38:23.000Z","msg":"二零零五年五月，在我穿上阿仙奴球衣的第一年，總算有點成績。自從林柏拉迪 (Liam Brady) 威脅要和我解約後，我的表現突飛猛進，在青年軍的十八場比賽中射入了十二球。我每週與一線隊訓練的時間漸漸變多了，有時甚至忘記了，自己只是和他們一起試訓而已。<br />\n<br />\n有一堂訓練課，我們在踢一場十一人比賽，規則是每次只能觸球兩下。我看到亨利 (Thierry Henry) 觸了球三下，就大叫「三下了！」。這時候，雲加 (Arsene Wenger) 的助教懷斯 (Pat Rice) 回喊：「屌你，繼續踢！」<br />\n<br />\n但亨利聽到了我的話，他轉過身來，把手指放到嘴唇邊：「殊。」<br />\n<br />\n沒多久之後，我做了一個和亨利一樣的觸球動作。在我傳球之前，皮球先碰到了我的腳跟，然後再碰到我的腳趾。作為青年軍的球員，就要被判罰球了。我當然不服氣，並開始抱怨，抱怨了很久，我說規則應該一視同仁。<br />\n<br />\n亨利叫我閉嘴，這句話裏還夾雜著很多粗口。事後回看，他當時其實提出了一個好提議，但我並沒有接受。我反擊他，說他才應該閉嘴。<br />\n<br />\n他向著我跑過來，面對面和我嚷著各式各樣的事情，他完全忽視了比賽還在進行。<br />\n<br />\n艾殊利高爾和蘇甘保留意到事情，就前來插手，他們說：「繼續踢球，尼克拉斯，閉嘴，跑起來。」我聽從了他們，事情回復了往常的平靜。<br />\n<br />\n但這並不是事情的結局，訓練結束後，亨利來找我了。我們開始交流，先是在更衣室，然後到球員休息室。我以前都不知道他那麼吹得，但顯然他能。他說了兩小時才把要說的話說完，不過對我來說。這只有一個小時長。<br />\n<br />\n他人真的很好，他根本沒必要和我說那麼多的。我聽取了他的建議，談話結束後，我們還擁抱了彼此。<br />\n<br />\n我以為事情就這麼圓滿解決了，但事實並非如此。之後的一個月，我再沒有和一線隊合練過，一次都沒有。<br />\n<br />\n等半年後，我再次回去和一線隊訓練時，我又發作了。這次跟我吵的是基拔圖施華 (Gilberto Silva)。他可以說是世界上最友善的人了，但嬲到上心口的我，差點就忘記了這一點。<br />\n<br />\n我本能地想叫他應該和亨利一樣閉嘴，不過謝天謝地，這次我控制了自己。我到現在還記得，我當時是怎麼說的：「閉上你的&hellip;&hellip;好的，基拔圖！」"},{"pid":"04c9f9bde2a960e94f2d66770462ea4b5ccbed29","tid":1694639,"uid":216975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:06:55.000Z","msg":"標題內文不符<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75708bfbfbe026bd8d73ddd4fea307d51dbfac0","tid":1694639,"uid":25100,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:21:18.000Z","msg":"屌你，繼續踢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd918ff436232c6ad08193e29e1e6f3c10cea0c","tid":1694639,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04c9f9bde2a960e94f2d66770462ea4b5ccbed29","tid":1694639,"uid":216975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:06:55.000Z","msg":"標題內文不符<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"邊度不乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b5af072589c8eb32aeafda03f086bdbbae6b51","tid":1694639,"uid":58242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e75708bfbfbe026bd8d73ddd4fea307d51dbfac0","tid":1694639,"uid":25100,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:21:18.000Z","msg":"屌你，繼續踢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"估唔到中文幾勁"},{"pid":"044a17fd32019756f8944f0fcc9011afa188cacd","tid":1694639,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"新潮文"},{"pid":"2d3c04d1ed758b86eefc7471f46231f1d2032b60","tid":1694639,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:47:26.000Z","msg":"亨利呢隻多嘴狗講波果時係咁屌雲加點點點，後尾去麼洛哥教波教到降班咁剩"},{"pid":"b1b1e58aeb3853fb23cfbd7d7803d26936513472","tid":1694639,"uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:48:17.000Z","msg":"亨利不嬲係鬼，我打fifa18個陣已經知"},{"pid":"661b53ba867c6b2de484d8c2e8e2dfc448dc3a4f","tid":1694639,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d3c04d1ed758b86eefc7471f46231f1d2032b60","tid":1694639,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:47:26.000Z","msg":"亨利呢隻多嘴狗講波果時係咁屌雲加點點點，後尾去麼洛哥教波教到降班咁剩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T10:59:53.000Z","msg":"後腦有反骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cab585994a16cf069f7bf743850d598ec4693a7","tid":1694639,"uid":54945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:17:05.000Z","msg":"賓特拿：16歲曾被男人性侵"},{"pid":"abdc5e1b77f6d37fd5e07191c6a5b36a941ead1f","tid":1694639,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"Nineup報？"},{"pid":"e5eeaad3aebc75ac2759d935719748f4dc59676a","tid":1694639,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"N_Ben<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53ae5e664b20812ae49fbf9e517305865c8d84e","tid":1694639,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abdc5e1b77f6d37fd5e07191c6a5b36a941ead1f","tid":1694639,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"Nineup報？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:10:44.000Z","msg":"自傳嚟"},{"pid":"4f322152611bfbd5a07ddb9621a3ebecdfbbe5be","tid":1694639,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"有冇防身鐵棍？"},{"pid":"cc2798e63d236bf533eb0bdad89d5c0fb2d20fda","tid":1694639,"uid":311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f322152611bfbd5a07ddb9621a3ebecdfbbe5be","tid":1694639,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"有冇防身鐵棍？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"防身鐵針"},{"pid":"b1369bf9245ff29163fbe3e98b92f945266e05a9","tid":1694639,"uid":25804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"巴塞-2屌唔屌得過"},{"pid":"388f87e97a5886c519d21f22a80762bdaead70ae","tid":1694639,"uid":25804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1369bf9245ff29163fbe3e98b92f945266e05a9","tid":1694639,"uid":25804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"巴塞-2屌唔屌得過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"Sor.錯post"},{"pid":"2db5ed12a7433316076481e994bd36780ca473b5","tid":1694639,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"閉上你的&hellip;&hellip;好的，基拔圖！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b52746c91fa1c57f582dc92d9876d3c281bd288","tid":1694639,"uid":39708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:15:32.000Z","msg":"如果佢同韋拉嘈會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c7d203e13a950b535d8ed73440c34183bef8c8","tid":1694639,"uid":3161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b52746c91fa1c57f582dc92d9876d3c281bd288","tid":1694639,"uid":39708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:15:32.000Z","msg":"如果佢同韋拉嘈會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:29:29.000Z","msg":"車路士前鋒安歷卡在自傳中爆出猛料，稱自己當初在阿仙奴時與韋拉產生矛盾，後者用生殖器抽打自己的臉部。韋拉的經紀人回應：&ldquo;這在我們國家是一種巨大的榮譽。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n安歷卡寫道：&ldquo;我在任何地方都不被接受。我在阿仙奴的職業生涯一帆風順，直到那天我惹到了韋拉，他在阿仙奴更衣室以&lsquo;長先生&rsquo;而聞名。那場是在高貝利對陣富咸，我記得是柏金傳球給我，我很輕鬆地過掉門將，那時已經是空門了，我卻在最後時刻把球踢偏了。因為太陽照著我的眼睛了，不是我的錯！韋拉盯著我，我知道自己麻煩了，之後沖涼完了他攻擊了我，我只是咬了他，我知道自己不該那樣，我還叫他&lsquo;瘦子焦炭人&rsquo;。一開始他用牛眼瞪著我，後來&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo; 好像他用老二抽了我的臉。只有一次，但是我還是嚇了一跳退了幾步。就好像被濕濕的醃魚抽打一樣。沒人相信自己的眼睛！你能想像自己在隊友眾目睽睽之下被一 根14寸的豬肉條抽打的景象嗎？那時我人生最糟糕的時刻，沒人說一句話，直到艾殊利高爾說&lsquo;是不是輪到我了&rsquo;，沉默才被打破。這時候我知道我要走了，雲加知道這件事之後盡然和他擊掌，喊道&lsquo;所以他才是隊長&rsquo;，靠，這算什麼事兒！&rdquo;隨後安歷卡透露自己直到加盟曼城與迪高夫搭檔才恢復了狀態。 <br />\n<br />\n韋拉的經紀人恩杜爾將安歷卡的書形容為&ldquo;羞恥&rdquo;，對於那件荒誕的事，他回應道：&ldquo;在我們國家那是一種巨大的榮譽，碰了韋拉的老二又怎樣？與其把我的東家刻畫成一個暴君，安歷卡先生更應該為用那張臭臉玷污我東家的老二而道歉。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"d19a524da848b16f6adedda47ba221eb27e15eca","tid":1694639,"uid":146447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:35:59.000Z","msg":"Lord賓係未以前試過飲醉酒屌死氣喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfe34c5ccd836cffde73f7604ed7b54c1e4f49d","tid":1694639,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1369bf9245ff29163fbe3e98b92f945266e05a9","tid":1694639,"uid":25804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"巴塞-2屌唔屌得過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"屌唔過"}]}